lead_paragraph: Manchester City manager Manuel Pellegrini was not surprised striker Kelechi Inheanacho marked a rare starting berth with a hat-trick in a 4-0 FA Cup rout of Aston Villa on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Inheanacho Shows City Have Firepower in Reserve
headline.main: Inheanacho Shows City Have Firepower in Reserve
